  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">We are operated entirely within the United States If you are located outside of the United States please note that any information including personal data that we collect about you will be transferred to and processed in the United States You hereby consent to these transfers</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

